title: Kiss - Detroit, Cobo Hall, MI 1983-02-23 (UPGRADE)
description:
Kiss
Cobo Arena
Detroit, MI
February 23, 1983
Creatures of the Night/10th Anniversary Tour

FLAC - Audience Recording
Lineage Unknown

Here's Kiss playing in their favorite city and venue during their final tour in makeup until 1996. It's a decent recording for this tour which didn't seem to offer up that many quality audios. 

Setlist:

Creatures of the Night
Detroit Rock City
Cold Gin
Calling Dr. Love
Paul Stanley Guitar Solo/I Want You/Vinnie Vincent Guitar Solo/I Want You (reprise)
I Love It Loud
Firehouse
Eric Carr Drum Solo
War Machine
Love Gun
Gene Simmons Bass Solo/God Of Thunder
I Still Love You
Black Diamond
Strutter
Rock And Roll All Nite



Enjoy!
